                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-648-18400203 t18400203-648-punishment-98"></join>Transported for Fourteen Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">TOYE</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18400203-648-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
